  "description": [
    "ARIZONAVRIBUNZ FRIDAY NOV 22 163 VOL 6 NO 19 EDWARD BANKS publishereditor ELOISE BANKS assistant editor BOBBY HEARD staff photographer ESTABLISHED JULY 10 1958 PUBLISHED EACH THURSDAY BY THE BANKS PUBLISHING COMPANY INC 2137 E BROADWAY ROAD 2762301 PHOENIX ARIZONA 85040 250 YR SECOND CLASS POSTAGE PAID AT PHOENiX ARIZONA all that is needed to remedy the evils OF OUR TIMES IS TO DO JUSTICE AND GIVE FREEDOM M h a member of NATIONAL REPRESENTATIVE AnrotiANEWSPAPEits Association amalgamated publishers Fr 6rMWf NWk Unkt NEW 1 YORK I7 A N E Y V i c According to the latest report from the Arizona State Employment Service there are not enough Negro applicants for the jobs which are available This is strange since there are so many persons who are unable to find jobs The state minority groups consultant Carl Craig urges all persons regardless of previous job experience to apply There are all kinds of openings in the area The Arizona Merit System is the clear ing house and testing and placement bu reau for the healthy welfare employment security and civil defense departments of the state Interested persons should contact Mr Craig for further information There are examinations given weekly"
